title: Britney Spears - Blackout (Collector's Edition)
description:
In celebration of the approaching 6th year anniversary release of "Blackout", I give you "Blackout: Collector's Edition". This is my 2 disc collection of 35 Official,Unreleased and demo tracks from the "Blackout" Sessions. Disc 1 is the Blackout album with some official, unmastered tracks. The 2nd disc is demos, unreleased and unmastered tracks. All in Mp3 format. All Britney. ENJOY!

Key
*(Studio) Unmastered tracks
*(Main) Mastered Tracks
*(Demo) Unfinished tracks
* (Demo)* Looped demo
*(Snippet) 8-10 Second Demo
